Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:38.63,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:91961,98634}{\i1}Egawa had offered Nozomi a chance to debut,\Nbut she turned it down. Was that a wise decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:43.01,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:98634,103013}{\i1}Nozomi had been eagerly awaiting\Nthe day when she could make her debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:45.80,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:103013,105808}{\i1}What changed her feelings was\Nseeing Kōda Miki's lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:105808,109103}{\i1}and how it makes her move away\Nfrom the world of music more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:57.90,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:112064,117903}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,2000,\1c&HD3F0CB&\3c&H020400&\4c&H000000&)}Good luck, Nozomi!\NCongratulations!{NOTE:がんばれ\\Nのぞみねえちゃん\\Nおめでとう}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:58.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:112106,118737}{\i1}However, the most difficult thing for Nozomi\Nwas facing her family, who did not know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:07.91,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:119905,127913}{\fad(1500,1500)}— Episode 20 —\NWelcome Back, Fanni{NOTE:第20話\\N返ってきたファニー}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.42,Default,Mine Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:133919,137423}I really don't think\NI can understand you.{NOTE:母さんはね やっぱり素直に賛成できないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.92,Default,Mine Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:138007,140926}You have come this far\Nand you want to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.38,Default,Mine Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:141427,143387}You did everything for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:28.47,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:145389,148475}What do you say, Nozomi?\NI could go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.52,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:148475,151520}How about talking\Nto Mr. Egawa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:36.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:151520,156442}I thought you of all people\Nwould understand my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.77,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:158694,160779}Hey, Nozomi-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.98,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:160779,161989}Actually, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:45.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:162531,165951}What does it mean to be a singer?\NWhat and whom do I sing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:49.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:165951,169496}Until I can answer these questions,\NI can't make my debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:54.12,Default,Mine Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:170122,174126}But you know, Nozomi, such a chance\Ndoesn't come your way every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:174126,175669}I'm well aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.88,Default,Mine Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:175669,177880}So why do you behave this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:02.25,Default,Mine Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:177880,182259}What's more, keep in mind that Mr. Egawa\Nhas gone out of his way to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:08.59,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:184386,188599}And here I was telling all my friends\Nthat you would go on television soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.10,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:189225,191101}Sis won't be a singer anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.60,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:191894,193604}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.39,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:194396,197399}Well, if you're so sure of yourself,\NI won't say anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.27,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:197399,199276}Just don't regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.36,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:199944,202363}One doesn't make a living\Nwith ideals alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:202363,203656}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:205783,208285}Kazuo-chan, Yuki-chan.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:209161,210788}It really means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.43,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:211872,213432}– Look, it's Fanni!\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:37.88,Default,TV,0,0,0,,{TIME:213716,217887}{\i1}The boxer Fanni Moriyama\Nreturns home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.30,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:217887,219305}{\an2}Welcome Home, Fanni Moriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:45.56,Default,TV,0,0,0,,{TIME:218512,225561}{\an8\i1}After mysterious disappearance\Nhe comes back with a world ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:50.56,Default,TV,0,0,0,,{TIME:225561,230566}{\an8\i1}When he first arrived to New York, he started\Nworking odd jobs to ensure his livelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:53.56,Default,TV,0,0,0,,{TIME:230566,233569}{\an8\i1}But he never stopped training as a boxer\Nand soon joined a local gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:04:03.91,Default,TV,0,0,0,,{TIME:233569,243913}{\an8\i1}And last month, he defeated the legendary\NTerry Wilson in a light weight title match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:219638,221682}{\i1}Fanni's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:223809,225811}{\i1}Fanni… That's my Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:239450,243913}{\i1}Fanni's back… with world ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.45,Default,TV,0,0,0,,{TIME:245831,247458}How does it feel to be a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.71,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:247458,250711}"Star"? I don't like\Nthe sound of it, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:19.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:254590,259428}{\i1}Fanni's a star. I, on the other hand,\Nhave destroyed my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:259428,262306}{\i1}Did I make the right call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:262306,264475}{\i1}Or was that a grave mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:28.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:265017,268103}{\i1}Fanni… What would you say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:268103,269355}{\i1}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.95,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:277988,280950}No, no! Stop pushing, for crying\Nout loud! He won't see anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:281617,282785}Sir, I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.82,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:282785,284828}Go home. Fanni doesn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:284828,286538}I am friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:286538,288791}Tell him that Mine Nozomi\Nwould like to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.29,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:288791,291293}Sorry, but no. He doesn't want\Nto see anyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:291293,293837}No way. Just tell him\Nmy name, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.38,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:293837,295381}No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:59.76,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:295381,299760}Chairman's Office{NOTE:会長室}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:02.34,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:300511,302346}Huh? Mine Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.93,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:302346,303931}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.93,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:304723,306934}I told you before.\NI don't want to see anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:07.81,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:306934,307810}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.69,Default,Chairman,0,0,0,,{TIME:311772,312690}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.40,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:312690,314400}No, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.19,Default,Chairman,0,0,0,,{TIME:316819,318195}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:06:00.02,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:355482,360029}{\i1}No one's heard of him before,\Nand now he's a legendary star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:363073,365826}{\i1}There's no way\Nhe'd want to meet you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:375377,377755}{\i1}Did Fanni change?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:377755,380549}{\i1}The Fanni I remember\Nwas kind and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:381592,383844}{\i1}Did I really make the right decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:383844,385262}{\i1}Tell me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.60,Default,Secretary,0,0,0,,{TIME:393937,395606}Sir, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:395981,397441}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:403572,407117}So, did you finish the lyrics\NI asked you for the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.87,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:413290,415876}I will be happy with anything,\Nas long as it is written by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:02.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:418879,422633}But if it's possible, I'd like it\Nto be a beautiful love song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:427721,429640}Oh, is this my song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.68,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:431308,432684}You are really rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:432684,434144}Rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.98,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:434144,437981}What and who I am writing for\Ndoes not concern you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:24.44,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:441610,444446}This one is for Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:444446,446031}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.86,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:446031,448867}Sometimes, you see, I write songs…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.58,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:451328,453580}…to hear them,\Nrather than sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:41.08,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:457126,461088}I wonder if Mine will ever agree\Nto sing this piece, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:464967,467386}You are unreasonably spiteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:467386,470889}Apparently you like Nozomi a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:54.05,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:470889,474059}Did you know that her boyfriend,\NFanni Moriyama, has returned home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.10,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:475018,476103}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:08:00.02,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:476103,480023}Fanni Moriyama.\NHe's became a star and now he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:480023,482109}You know what they organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.69,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:482109,483694}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.36,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:483694,485362}A welcome party for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.78,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:485362,487781}A welcome party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.78,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:487781,489783}Fanni Moriyama…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.74,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:494413,496748}It's at Hotel United.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.79,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:501378,502796}{\i1}Fanni Moriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:27.38,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:502796,507384}{\i1}What kind of man is he? Who could\Npossibly make her fall head over heels?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.89,Default,Office lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:513432,516894}Here, the elevator to the 39th floor,\Nthe Sky Hall is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:48.86,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:524651,528864}Fanni Moriyama is a big deal.\NI bet he'll become big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.15,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:528864,530157}I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.99,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:530157,532993}I only saw him on TV,\Nbut he's handsome, like an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.04,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:539291,543045}{\fad(1500,0)}Fanni Moriyama Welcome Party{NOTE:ファニー森山帰国パーティー}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:550260,552554}I am not a fan.\NI know Fanni personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.68,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:552888,554681}"Fanni"…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:554681,557476}I kindly ask you to let me see\NFanni Moriyama-san in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.43,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:557476,560437}Sorry, but this party\Nis invitation only.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.39,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:560437,563398}– Excuse me…\N– Oh, welcome, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:594596,597182}{\i1}Fanni… Why did you become a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.56,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:602229,604564}Oh, I forgot my invitation.\NLet's do the formalities later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:07.52,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:604564,607526}Ah, Mr. Nohara!\NPlease enjoy the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:13.74,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:607859,613740}Here is Saeki Yumi-san, No. 1 among beautiful\Nactresses. She wanted to meet Fanni by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.03,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:613740,616034}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nlet's have a round of applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.29,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:619121,621290}Thanks, thanks.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:24.62,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:621290,624626}Well then, ladies and gentlemen,\Nthe drinks and meals are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:29.29,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:624626,629298}We hope you enjoy this party and celebrate\NFanni Moriyama's return with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.92,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:629923,632926}Pleased to meet you.\NMy name is Nohara Jun. I'm a song writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.59,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:632926,634594}I'm Fanni Moriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.80,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:636179,637806}Let's talk over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.05,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:638765,641059}Actually, I came to talk to you\Nabout Mine Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:42.01,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:641059,642019}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.35,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:642686,644354}About… Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:50.15,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:644354,650152}I have a genuine feelings for her song, or her\Npassion for it. You could say I'm in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.77,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:650152,652779}How… does that concern me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.61,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:652779,654614}She's smitten with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.90,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:654614,655907}She loves you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.78,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:655907,658785}I'm here to ask about\Nyour feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:03.37,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:659328,663373}I want to know how you\Ngenuinely feel about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.41,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:663373,665417}I'd rather not talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.29,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:665417,668295}So are you saying that you do not\Nhave any feelings for Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.17,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:669212,670172}That's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.09,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:671798,674092}Nozomi has been\Nwaiting for your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.05,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:674092,676053}Look, what do you expect me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:23.18,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:676678,683185}Even as a boxer, you ought to know how important\Nit is for her as a singer to maintain that purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:27.18,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:683185,687189}She's very talented and I think it's your job\Nas her lover to protect her innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.06,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:687189,688065}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.56,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:689524,690567}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.90,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:691401,693904}It's not my concern if Nozomi\Nis too weak to face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:38.07,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:693904,698075}I don't care whether\Nshe sings your songs, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.07,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:698950,701078}Hold on! She's still just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.07,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:701453,702079}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.08,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:702996,705082}Are you just going\Nto throw her out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.24,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:705082,706249}Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.58,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:706249,709586}How could I abandon\Nmy little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.17,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:710545,711171}Little sister?…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:711713,713048}Little sister?
Comment: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:05.31,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:725310,725310}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:742561,744479}Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:42.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:754781,762080}If you were to get lyrics from Nohara-san,\Nwouldn't you be so kind to sell them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:42.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:762080,762747}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:765125,767419}Is this what you\Nwanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:767419,769254}I'd be very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:771339,774759}Is Nohara-san composing\Na song for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.59,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:775552,777596}Could you sell them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:781099,783018}I have to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:786271,787981}It's not out of any malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:15.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:790317,795530}If he wrote a song for me,\Nwouldn't it be rude to him to peddle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.15,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:795530,797157}Get off your high horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:797157,801203}I only offered it because I thought\Nit would be a waste on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.91,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:803079,807918}Don't you get that a good song should\Nbe sold in stores all over the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:808627,809461}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:36.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:812506,816384}But you always preach about the essence\Nof music or whatever. What a load of garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.13,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:816384,818136}What have you accomplished so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:818136,819804}It is not garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:44.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:819804,824976}I do want to become a real singer. I am just\Nstill figuring out what that means to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:824976,827270}Look, there are no real singers\Nor fake singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:51.48,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:827270,831483}Professionals have to produce as many hits\Nas possible. That is all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:832192,834569}But it doesn't mean\Nthe end justifies the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:834569,838031}Fine, whatever.\NI get so irritated whenever I talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:838031,840033}Will you sell it to me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:840033,841993}I will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:860762,862889}I'm sorry.\NI guess that was out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.39,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:865058,867394}Did you see Fanni already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:28.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:868228,868895}Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.85,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:869688,871856}I suppose you weren't able to.\NSuch a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:871856,874067}Huh? How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:878655,880740}Miki-san, if you know\Nsomething, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:880740,883034}Oh, I do happen to know something.\NSomething truly unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:883034,884995}What is it? Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.62,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:886663,888623}Fanni and you\Nare brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:890500,894337}If you think I'm lying,\Ntry asking him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.55,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:902262,904556}{\i1}Fanni and you\Nare brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:911771,913982}{\i1}Fanni is my older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.44,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:917527,919446}The hell?! You have a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:932459,934669}{\i1}Fanni is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:943762,945013}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:945013,946181}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:949476,951394}Open up, Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:951394,952937}Please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:952937,953938}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:953938,956191}Open the door.\NI'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:956191,957817}Please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:957817,960362}Fanni, you're there,\Naren't you? Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.98,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:960362,961988}Go away, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.49,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:963239,964491}We can't see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:970997,972957}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:972957,974084}Are you my…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.62,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:974084,975627}Don't say it out loud, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:980256,982509}Are you really…\NAre you my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.51,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:982509,984511}Calm down, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.77,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:991893,993770}So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.10,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:993770,995105}What do you say, Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.27,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:995105,998274}Forget about it as soon as possible\Nand dedicate yourself to singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018253,1019170}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019838,1021381}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033309,1036229}The Fanni I loved was my brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036229,1037564}It can't be. It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048742,1051703}{\i1}Now I remember, back then\NI had been looking for Hisashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051703,1055623}{\i1}I couldn't see him anywhere.\NI didn't even know how he looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055623,1057709}{\i1}But I found Fanni instead…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067761,1070638}{\i1}Fanni was my brother\NHisashi all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070638,1074309}{\i1}The man I had loved\Nwas my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.19,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081733,1083193}Fanni Moriyama speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.11,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083193,1085111}{\i1}This is Nohara.\NSorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.11,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085111,1087113}{\i1}To cut things short,\NI'm looking for Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.69,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087113,1088698}What? Did something\Nhappen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:12.99,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089574,1092994}Yes. As far as I know,\Nshe went to see you, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:15.24,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092994,1095246}she didn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.33,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095246,1096331}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.70,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096331,1098708}{\i1}I'm doing what I can to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.16,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099292,1101169}I understand.\NI'll go look for her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:27.42,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102962,1107425}You're so infatuated with Nozomi\Nthat you get angry when it comes to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:31.38,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107425,1111387}How can you go around hurting people\Nwithout feeling any sort of remorse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.84,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111387,1114849}Hurting each other\Nis the destiny of all rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:40.52,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115725,1120522}How is Nozomi your rival when she\Ngave up her chance to make a debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.98,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120522,1121981}Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:45.86,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121981,1125860}You do not believe in yourself,\Nand that's why you're afraid of Nozomi.
